<ptxt>
<emph>
P0500: Vehicle Speed Sensor “A”
</emph>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Any of the following conditions is met.
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Vehicle speed is slower than 4 km/h (2.5 mile/h) for 4 sec. at fuel cut.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Vehicle speed is not input by CAN communication.
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
<ptxt>
(2 D/C detection logic)
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
